{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act33side", "eventName": "巴別塔", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BB-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "陰影顯現", "storyInfo": "經營多年後，特雷西斯終於準備親自前往倫蒂尼姆。阿斯卡綸試圖阻攔卻無功而返，特蕾西婭則堅信巴別塔的未來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g3_kazdelstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1094年初"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，卡茲戴爾移動城市"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8, "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請等等，將軍！", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你太浮躁了。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是！那位公爵的使者幾乎是打算把唾沫吐在——", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得到想要的了嗎？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確拿到了部分工業區的使用權和邊境通行權……但一定要以那樣屈辱的方式嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的公爵對您呼來喝去，把薩卡茲當作順從的野獸，那些從內戰中抬起頭來的戰士們等待的並不是今天，將軍！", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是正如我們所願？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道我們想要維多利亞從一開始就把薩卡茲當作最大的敵人，然後團結一致來對付我們？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是您的……我知道示敵以弱的必要性，可這……", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們之中的很多人，認為這毫不榮耀——", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我許諾他們的，是榮耀嗎？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人眼裡的薩卡茲，有榮耀嗎？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德，你最近太急躁了。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……尊嚴很重要，曼弗雷德。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會為戰士們打抱不平，也會有人因此而尊敬你。若是平常，也許我會誇讚你。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在，我們在做什麼？在準備竊取一個國家的心臟。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在瓦解這片大地上最強大的帝國。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的隔閡令他們脆弱不堪，而薩卡茲正飢腸轆轆。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們需要的本就不是“榮耀”“尊敬”。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我明白。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的軍隊準備得如何了？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整裝待發。先行的同胞會在倫蒂尼姆接應我們。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快就是卡文迪許公爵要求我們抵達的最後期限，我們隨時可以出發。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們啟程，去毀滅維多利亞。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g7_councilchamber", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們一直在值守？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "軍事委員會衛士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先退下吧，我想一個人待一下子。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，長官。", "name": "軍事委員會衛士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_opencabinet", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "待守衛離去，曼弗雷德取出放在一旁的酒杯。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openwindow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來一杯嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以前從不喝酒。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在也不喝。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是將軍命令我學習維多利亞人的“禮儀”，為接下來的任務做準備。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在才知道，原來那些貴族吃一頓飯需要搭配好幾種酒，每種酒還要搭配不同的杯子。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得嗎？小時候將軍領著我們去古戰場練劍……晚上天氣冷，將軍煮了湯才發現我們沒有盛湯的東西。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過戰場四處都散落著炮彈殼，你就用它們削了四隻杯子。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、我、將軍還有殿下，就端著彈殼做的杯子，圍坐在篝火前。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得，很安靜的一夜。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就和現在一樣。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殘冬冰涼的月光落進窗戶，曼弗雷德的手按上劍柄，也是一樣的冰涼。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空氣裡靜極了，兩人都可以聽到彼此的心跳。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們明天就會去倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你想見將軍。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該沒見到，不然也不會到我這來。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我放棄了。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我發現自己遠遠看到他的第一眼，腦海冒出的念頭是，我現在應該動手殺了他。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你應該慶幸自己保住了一絲理性。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你現在來找我？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說你的劍術水準提升很多，讓我看看。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#10$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來都打不過你。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒倒下，就別求饒。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有次我們在特蕾西婭殿下的書房裡面打架。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一整面牆的書都落了下來，將軍收走了我們的武器，限我們在半個小時內將書房恢復原樣。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道當時你是故意的，你想引起兩位殿下的注意。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_flashpowerful", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.5, "duration": 0.1}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸身形一晃，眨眼間匿入陰影中。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_daggerexsheath", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1", "focus": "none", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再一眨眼，曼弗雷德便感受到自己頸側劃過一絲涼意。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他沒有拔出劍來抵抗，甚至沒有來得及生出抵抗的念頭。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是太疲憊了嗎？"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我在這裡劃開你的脖子，至少可以讓你不用死在倫蒂尼姆，我會把你的屍體扔進熔爐裡。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……也可以讓很多人不用死在異國他鄉的戰場上。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你下定決心的話，應該立刻殺了我，這是你最後的機會。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想好了。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍說你缺少自己的信念，我覺得不盡然。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "性命被別人威脅的時候，不該有這麼多話。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到最近我才明白，我並不比你堅定。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都是被看不見的浪潮推到了這一步……可是從戰爭開始的那天起，我們就都沒有回頭路了。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就……盡量活下去吧。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一次，我不會收手的。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_darkmagic", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.95, "focus": "none", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "none", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉默的刺客收起了袖刃，緩緩退回陰影中。"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我也是。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願這是我們的最後一次見面。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g14_rhodesdeck_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，巴別塔羅德島本艦"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一陣寒風將殘冬厚實的雲層吹散，陽光從裂隙間穿過，鋪在艦橋上。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "台階下，阿斯卡綸站在護欄旁一動不動。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她緊閉雙目，享受陽光帶來的片刻暖意。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "台階上，一陣織物摩擦地面的窸窣聲傳來。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過路者的影子晃過刺客的面龐，遮住了從天空灑下的陽光。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,-20", "posto": "0,-20", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我打擾到你休息了嗎，阿斯卡綸？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為把鞋子脫掉走路，就不會有什麼聲音了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，無論何時，都不會打擾。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#10$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地上很冷，您得趕快把鞋穿好。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,-28", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-28", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就不想和我說說嗎，阿斯卡綸？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下指的是？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你回卡茲戴爾的事。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是我擅自做的決定。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想您是不同意的，我不知道要怎麼主動向殿下您開口……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會呢，阿斯卡綸？既然是你的決定，我也會相信你的判斷。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你見到他們了嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他和曼弗雷德都很好。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信。他們都是很強大的人。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也該做好準備，奪回卡茲戴爾的作戰不會太遠了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為何你的眉頭反而鎖得更緊了？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們最近的作戰計劃很激進，在各個戰場都取得了不少戰果……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我總是會感到一種不安。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴別塔變化很多，尤其是……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士變了很多，行事作風更加高效，更加冷靜，就像……一台不會有差錯的機器。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一位指揮官應當具備的品質，為什麼反而讓你擔憂呢？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起現在這位優秀的指揮官……我更信任那個會從馱獸背上狼狽滾下來的傢伙。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下，現在真的是進攻卡茲戴爾的好時機嗎？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的直覺總是很準確。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下也憂慮過？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#2$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，你不記得了嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些年，有多少次，我們遇上了看上去萬萬無法克服的絕境。可最終，我們都一一跨了過來。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想接下來，也是一樣的。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們始終是在冒險……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸，巴別塔是背負了許多人的希望、信念才走到今天的，我們沒有辦法停在原地。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與軍事委員會的對抗，我們始終落於下風。眼下，他們的主力部隊大多前往了倫蒂尼姆，這是絕無僅有的機會。我們沒有選擇。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定會在您身旁，保護好您的安全。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，阿斯卡綸。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將來，你一定要去更遠的地方，去保護更多人。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，放鬆一下，曬一會太陽吧。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，記得不要總是站著小憩，疲勞時還是該回房間好好睡一覺。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會記住的。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#10$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陽光重新回到阿斯卡綸的臉上。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明媚，暖和。可方才在影子移去的那刻，她卻突然感到自胸口泛出一絲異樣。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時她尚不能體會，多年後，某個陽光正好的日子裡，她才突然醒悟。"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是不捨。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g4_giantwall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞，倫蒂尼姆"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傭兵！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳公爵的口諭，這次攻入倫蒂尼姆，你們做得不錯。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個小時後在中央城區集結，在那裡接受檢閱，領取你們的賞金。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……喂！聽到命令了嗎？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我已收到命令。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請代我向公爵回覆，我們會按時趕到的。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……薩卡茲感謝他的慷慨。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裝模作樣的魔族佬……", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是硝煙彌漫，今天本該是倫蒂尼姆難得的好天氣。站在高聳的城牆上，這座古老城市的風景可以一覽無遺。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰袍染血的將軍一言不發，他的眼神緊盯著城市中央，那座高聳的大廈。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆的天空，飄過了一片烏雲。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}